cks":["This delicious bread is perfect for sharing; serve fresh from the oven for the best flavour and texture.","To reheat, wrap the bread in greaseproof paper or baking paper, and warm in the oven at 150°C for 15 minutes.","Replace the Gorgonzola with another blue cheese such as Stilton, Dolcelatte or Cambozola."],"basicInfo":["easy","15m","40m","6 portions"]}